wiki/Erice\" title=\"Erice\">Floating above the clouds on Sicily’s western coast, Erice has been a place of pilgrimage for millennia — from an ancient Temple of Venus to the medieval churches that remain open today.</a></div>\n\t</section></section></div>\n\t<p><span class=\"nolink\" typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\" data-mw=\"{&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Erice&quot;}\"><span title=\"Erice\"><img alt=\"Erice\" resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/thumb/3/39/OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png/1920px-OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"3034\" data-file-height=\"1010\" data-file-type=\"bitmap\" height=\"566\" width=\"1700\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/3/39/OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/3/39/OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png 2x\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></span></span>\n\t<span typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\" data-mw=\"{&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Erice&quot;}\"><a href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Erice\" title=\"Erice\"><img alt=\"Erice\" resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/thumb/3/39/OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png/1920px-OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"3034\" data-file-height=\"1010\" data-file-type=\"bitmap\" height=\"566\" width=\"1700\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/3/39/OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/3/39/OtBT-Erice-bannerA.png 2x\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></p>\n</div>","link":"https://en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Previously_Off_the_beaten_path","retrieved":1761269123153},{"title":"Featured Travel Topic (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r4523569\" about=\"#mwt11\" typeof=\"mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion\" data-mw=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;templatestyles&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;Banner/